sql.query:
SELECT
            c.customerID,
            c.customerName,
            c.contact,
            CASE 
                WHEN COUNT(o.orderID) OVER (PARTITION BY c.customerID) > 0 THEN TRUE 
                ELSE FALSE 
            END AS has_orders
        FROM demo_etl.customers c 
        LEFT JOIN demo_etl.orders o ON c.customerID = o.customerID

SELECT
            c.customerID,
            c.customerName,
            c.contact,
            CASE 
                WHEN COUNT(o.orderID) OVER (PARTITION BY c.customerID) > 0 THEN TRUE 
                ELSE FALSE 
            END AS has_orders
        FROM demo_etl.customers c 
        LEFT JOIN demo_etl.orders o ON c.customerID = o.customerID

SELECT
            productID,
            productName,
            price,
            CASE 
                WHEN price > 0 THEN TRUE 
                ELSE FALSE 
            END AS is_in_stock
        FROM demo_etl.products

SELECT
            o.customerID,
            s.orderID,
            s.productID,
            p.productName,
            s.quantity,
            p.price * s.quantity as total_amount   
        FROM demo_etl.sales s 
        JOIN demo_etl.orders o ON s.orderID = o.orderID
        JOIN demo_etl.products p ON s.productID = p.productID
        WHERE quantity > 0

SELECT
            o.customerID,
            s.orderID,
            s.productID,
            p.productName,
            s.quantity,
            p.price * s.quantity as total_amount   
        FROM demo_etl.sales s 
        JOIN demo_etl.orders o ON s.orderID = o.orderID
        JOIN demo_etl.products p ON s.productID = p.productID
        WHERE quantity > 0

SELECT
            s.customerID,
            SUM(s.total_amount) AS total_spent,
            COUNT(s.orderID) AS total_orders
        FROM demo_etl.sales_enriched s 
        GROUP BY customerID

SELECT
            s.productID,
            SUM(s.quantity) AS total_units_sold,
            SUM(s.total_amount) AS total_revenue
        FROM demo_etl.sales_enriched s
        JOIN demo_etl.products_enriched p ON s.productID = p.productID
        GROUP BY s.productID

SELECT
            s.productID,
            SUM(s.quantity) AS total_units_sold,
            SUM(s.total_amount) AS total_revenue
        FROM demo_etl.sales_enriched s
        JOIN demo_etl.products_enriched p ON s.productID = p.productID
        GROUP BY s.productID
